IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jvillasantegomez@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass Logins/google.com"
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.Maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/.Maildir/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *